      "date": "2013-02-05 06:12:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> Tests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/6fe1e112-6cfb-11e2-83d0-52540035b04c). Ran 2 tests. 1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.\n\nThis test session was run with zfs backend filesystem and failed with LU-2733. The issue was fixed on the latest master branch.",
